Package edu.uga.cs.recdawgs.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Administrator
    This class represents an Administrator user in the RecDawgs system.
    League
    This class represents a sports league in the RecDawgs system.
    Match
    This class represents a match between two teams participating in the same sports league.
    Round
    This class represents a round of matches played in some sports league.
    ScoreReport
    This class represents a score report for a match between two teams in a sports league.
    SportsVenue
    This class represents a sports venue for playing matches.
    Student
    This class represents information about a registered student of in the RecDawgs system.
    Team
    This class represents a recreational sports team, participating in one of the sports leagues.
    User
    This is the base class of all registered users of the RecDawgs system.
